data.text:
The boys followed up their first top ten hit with this re-release of their first hit, which proved to be their biggest.

It was a new entry on this day in the 80s, at #45, and would eventually make it all the way to UK#2 and US#23.

It would be the last time they were in the top 20 though, and it was their only US hit.
